    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/06d2199d7308a1c9f2795f32ae7ca6a5.poster.avif?t=1769624388\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/06d2199d7308a1c9f2795f32ae7ca6a5.webm?t=1769624388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/06d2199d7308a1c9f2795f32ae7ca6a5.mp4?t=1769624388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FLING YOURSELF INTO DANGER!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master a dynamic <i><strong>momentum-based</strong></i> movement system. Line up multiple enemies to execute a flurry of precise <i><strong>tackles </strong></i>dealing devastating damage while bouncing between a barrage of enemy bullets! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/8de4ab0f4d86213c59d2c7c695f7830f.poster.avif?t=1769624388\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/8de4ab0f4d86213c59d2c7c695f7830f.webm?t=1769624388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/8de4ab0f4d86213c59d2c7c695f7830f.mp4?t=1769624388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HACK YOUR SHIP!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize the limited <i><strong>inventory</strong></i> your cockpit provides to optimize your build! <i><strong>Upgrade</strong></i>, <i><strong>integrate</strong></i>, and even <i><strong>fuse</strong></i> <i><strong>hacks</strong></i> together to create varied builds every run. <i><strong>Fusing</strong></i> empowers players to discover secret handmade <i><strong>synergies</strong></i> or to find a combo of stats and abilities that is entirely their own. Cleverly manipulate the shop, hack positioning, action order, and even your negative stats to get as much out of your build as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/9e3415aa36975f79c2d6377333c1b4e5.poster.avif?t=1769624388\" width=616 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/9e3415aa36975f79c2d6377333c1b4e5.webm?t=1769624388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184290/extras/9e3415aa36975f79c2d6377333c1b4e5.mp4?t=1769624388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SELECT YOUR LOADOUT!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game-plan before each run, Select a <i><strong>pilot</strong></i> and a <i><strong>ship</strong></i>! Your choice of <i><strong>pilot</strong></i> grants you a powerful passive ability! While your ship, of which also comes with its own powerful passive, additionally determines your starting place for over 10+ stats!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROGRESSION! [OUR WAY]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 4 things to unlock in Rising Heat - <i><strong>Ships</strong></i>, <i><strong>Pilots</strong></i>, <i><strong>Hacks</strong></i>, and <i><strong>Maps</strong></i>! There is zero progression-based stat creep!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FLY WITH A FRIEND</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In co-op mode, both players have their ships connected by a deadly energy beam. While the beam can be used to destroy enemies, uncoordinated movement can yank your wingman into danger.</p>",
